          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Neutron bursts were produced by modulation of",
                "the arc source of a small cyclotron. Neutrons",
                "subsequently slowed down in paraffin were detected by",
                "a BF3 ionization chamber and linear amplifier.",
                "Modulation of an additional amplifier allowed the",
                "counting of all detected neutrons as well as those",
                "arriving in a specified time interval. Time of flight",
                "experiments were carried out at 3.0 meters with \"on\"",
                "times of 50 or 100 microsec (microseconds) out of a",
                "period of 2500 microsec."
              ]
            }
          ],
